# Cloud Build only needs the Dockerfile, the entrypoint script, and the
# build configs. The actual openclaw runtime comes from the upstream base
# image (ghcr.io/openclaw/openclaw:<version>) so we deliberately do not
# upload the rest of the repo.
#
# .gitignore-style: `*` excludes everything; `!` re-includes. Re-including
# a file inside an excluded directory requires re-including the directory
# first, so we take a two-step approach for `scripts/`.

*

!Dockerfile.cloudrun
!cloudbuild.yaml
!cloudbuild.build.yaml

!scripts
scripts/*
!scripts/cloudrun-entrypoint.sh
